{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"stylesheet.href","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/href","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>Stylesheet</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/disabled\"><code>disabled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/href\"><code>href</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/media\"><code>media</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet/ownerNode\"><code>ownerNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/parentStyleSheet\"><code>parentStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/type\"><code>type</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Zwraca położenie zewnetrznego arkusza stylów.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><i>uri</i> = stylesheet.href\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>uri</code> jest łańcuchem zawierającym URI arkusza stylów.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad","title":"Przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"> // W lokalnej maszynie:\n &lt;html&gt;\n  &lt;head&gt;\n   &lt;link rel=\"StyleSheet\" href=\"example.css\" type=\"text/css\" /&gt;\n   &lt;script&gt;\n    function sref() {\n     alert(document.styleSheets[0].href);\n    }\n   &lt;/script&gt;\n  &lt;/head&gt;\n  &lt;body&gt;\n   &lt;div class=\"thunder\"&gt;Thunder&lt;/div&gt;\n   &lt;button onclick=\"sref()\"&gt;ss&lt;/button&gt;\n  &lt;/body&gt;\n &lt;/html&gt;\n// Zwraca \"file:////C:/Windows/Desktop/example.css\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notatki","title":"Notatki","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Jeżeli arkusz stylów jest zewnętrznym arkuszem stylów, wartością tego atrybutu jest jego lokalizacja. Dla wewnętrznego arkusza stylów, wartość tego atrybutu wynosi null.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Style-20001113/stylesheets.html#StyleSheets-StyleSheet-href\" rel=\" noopener\">href </a></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Zwraca położenie zewnetrznego arkusza stylów.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Stylesheet.href","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stylesheet.href","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Stylesheet.href","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"StyleSheet.href","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"href","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/stylesheet/href","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/stylesheet/href/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/Stylesheet/href","title":"stylesheet.href"}],"pageTitle":"stylesheet.href - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}